OL,5,Cremoval
OL,7,FITV Granada Reports journalist Tim
OL,8,FScott spoke to those affected by
OL,9,Fcladding removal
OL,11,FA man says his life is a "living hell"
OL,12,Fafter his home was left with exposed
OL,13,Fwires and no insulation - four years
OL,14,Fafter his flat block was stripped of
OL,15,Fdangerous cladding.
OL,17,FEddie Farrell is still waiting for
OL,18,Frepair work to take place on his flat
OL,19,Fafter efforts to make it safe by
OL,20,Fremoving the potentially dangerous
OL,21,Fcladding overran multiple times.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
