OL,5,Cremoval
OL,7,FHe says the flats, at Malus Court in
OL,8,FSalford, are still unsafe and the work
OL,9,Fhas made them an unpleasant
OL,10,Fenvironment to live in.
OL,12,F"There's holes all over the place,
OL,13,Fwe've been infested with mice and
OL,14,Frats, so if they can get in, smoke can
OL,15,Fget in, fire can get in.
OL,17,F"The company, Pendleton Together, just
OL,18,Fdon't seem to be doing anything about
OL,19,Fit, they're not listening to you, or
OL,20,Fignoring you.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
