OL,7,F"We feel as if we're dumped."
OL,9,FIt comes as a report by the National
OL,10,FAudit Office (NAO) found more than
OL,11,F7,000 buildings across England with
OL,12,Fdangerous cladding are yet to be
OL,13,Fidentified.
OL,15,FThe figure is thought to account for
OL,16,Fmore than a quarter of a million
OL,17,Findividual homes.
