OL,7,FThe NAO has warned completing works to
OL,8,Fmake all buildings safe at an
OL,9,Festimated cost of #16 billion might
OL,10,Fnot be achieved in the next decade.
OL,12,FEddie says he has a document from
OL,13,Fhousing operator Pendleton Together
OL,14,Fwhich states remedial work should have
OL,15,Fbeen finished two years ago.
OL,17,FBut he says he does not know when it
OL,18,Fwill be over.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
