OL,7,F"It's effected my whole life, the
OL,8,Fstrain of it all, things not getting
OL,9,Fdone, we're constantly getting on the
OL,10,Fphone, speaking to people, we've gone
OL,11,Fto council meetings.
OL,13,F"We're just getting ignored, you get
OL,14,Fthe same knock back, knock back, knock
OL,15,Fback.
OL,17,F"You begin to say 'it's the usual', no
OL,18,Fmatter what you ask, you get no
OL,19,Fpermanent answer, no direct answer."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
