OL,7,FCladding campaigner Giles Grover says
OL,8,Fwith so many stakeholders involved in
OL,9,Fthe cladding issue, problems just
OL,10,Fmultiply.
OL,12,FHe is calling on the government to
OL,13,Fstep up.
OL,15,F"It's the fact that people are still
OL,16,Fin unsafe homes and are struggling to
OL,17,Ffind out when their homes will be made
OL,18,Fsafe," he said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
