OL,7,F"Pre-holders, developers, housing
OL,8,Fassociations, managed agents,
OL,9,Fcontractors, they're all focused on
OL,10,Ftheir own liability.
OL,12,F"They're all focused on covering their
OL,13,Fbacksides rather than making people's
OL,14,Fhomes safe, and that's where the
OL,15,Fgovernment really needs to get a grip.
OL,17,F"This government now, this new
OL,18,Fgovernment has a chance to develop
OL,19,Fmeaningful change and say 'right we're
OL,20,Fgoing to fix this mess'."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
