OL,7,FPendleton Together say work on Eddie's
OL,8,Fblock will finish in summer 2025, and
OL,9,Fsaid it shares the frustration over
OL,10,Fhow long the work has gone on.
OL,12,FMichelle Allott, Executive Director
OL,13,Ffor Operations at Together Housing
OL,14,FGroup, said: "Firstly, can I reiterate
OL,15,Fmy sincere apologies for the
OL,16,Fdisruption caused to our residents by
OL,17,Fthe ongoing programme of fire safety
OL,18,Fworks.
