OL,7,F"I share their frustration with the
OL,8,Ftime this is taking, but it is
OL,9,Fimportant that we get this right for
OL,10,Fthe safety and peace of mind for all
OL,11,Four residents.
OL,13,F"We have worked hard to ensure we
OL,14,Fachieve a solution that is compliant
OL,15,Fnot only with current but also
OL,16,Fpotential future guidance and that we
OL,17,Fdon't pass on any of the associated
OL,18,Fcosts to residents.
