OL,7,F"It is regrettable that during these
OL,8,Fworks there are noise and cosmetic
OL,9,Fdisturbances. We offer respite to all
OL,10,Four residents while noisy work is
OL,11,Ftaking place.
OL,13,F"While suspended ceilings are removed,
OL,14,Fpipework and wires are visible and,
OL,15,Fwhile we accept that this doesn't look
OL,16,Fattractive, they are assessed daily to
OL,17,Fensure that they don't present any
OL,18,Fkind of risk.
